Saber is a fanatic [[warforged]] follower of the [[Lord of Blades]], operating in [[Sharn]]. He is leading a team of operatives sent to the City of Towers to steal House [[Cannith]] documents and recover a long-lost [[schema]]. [[Cutter]] is one of his underlings.